msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid ""
"Antialiasing:Enables a technique to improve the appearance of high-contrast "
"edges.\n"
"\n"
"MSAA: Performs antialiasing by generating an intermediate high-resolution "
"image. Looks best, but doesn't cope with some settings.\n"
"\n"
"FXAA: Performs antialiasing by smoothing artifacts out as a post-process.|"
"Off|MSAA 2x|4x|FXAA"
msgstr ""
"Antialiasing:Habilita una técnica para mejorar la apariencia de los bordes "
"de alto contraste.\n"
"\n"
"MSAA: Realiza el antialiasing generando una imagen intermedia de alta "
"resolución. Se ve mejor, pero no es compatible con algunos ajustes.\n"
"\n"
"FXAA: Realiza el antialiasing suavizando los artefactos como un post-"
"proceso.|Off|MSAA 2x|4x|FXAA"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:132
#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:206
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Global Illumination"
msgstr "Iluminación global"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:134
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid ""
"Enables a physically based simulation of light path for more realistic "
"lighting."
msgstr ""
"Permite una simulación física en base a la trayectoria de la luz para una "
"iluminación más realista."

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:138
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Linear HDR Rendering"
msgstr "Renderizado HDR lineal"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:139
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid ""
"Uses a number representation which allows wider dynamic range during "
"rendering process. Additionally, this allows color calculation whose value "
"is in linear correspondence with actual energy, that is, physically accurate "
"blending can be achieved."
msgstr ""
"Utiliza una representación numérica que permite un rango dinámico más amplio "
"durante el proceso de renderizado. Además, permite calcular el color cuyo "
"valor está en correspondencia lineal con la energía real, es decir, se puede "
"lograr una mezcla físicamente precisa."

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:146
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid ""
"Vertical Sync:Synchronizes screen updates to a monitor's refresh rate.|Off|"
"On|Adaptive"
msgstr ""
"Sincronización vertical:Sincroniza las actualizaciones de la pantalla con la "
"frecuencia de actualización del monitor.|Apagado|Encendido|Adaptable"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:152
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Camera Blur"
msgstr "Desenfoque de cámara"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:153
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Blurs the screen when you turn quickly."
msgstr "Desenfoca la pantalla cuando te giras rapidamente."

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:156
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Lens Scattering Filter"
msgstr "Filtro de dispersión en el lente"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:157
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Simulates light being scattered by dust on the camera lens."
msgstr "Simula la luz siendo dispersada por el polvo en el lente de la cámara."

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:160
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Lens Flare"
msgstr "Destellos de lente"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:161
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "The Sun causes lens flare."
msgstr "El Sol causa un destello de lente."

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:164
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Flares for Dynamic Lights."
msgstr "Destellos para luces dinámicas."

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:165
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Enables lens flare for light sources other than the Sun."
msgstr "Activa destello de lente para otras fuentes de luz diferentes al Sol."

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:168
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Color Correction"
msgstr "Corrección de color"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:169
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Applies cinematic color correction to make the image look better."
msgstr ""
"Aplica una corrección de color cinematográfica para que la imagen tenga "
"mejor aspecto."

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:172
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Depth of Field"
msgstr "Profundidad de campo"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:173
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Blurs out-of-focus objects."
msgstr "Difumina los objetos fuera del foco."

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:176
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Screen Space Ambient Occlusion"
msgstr "Oclusión ambiental de espacio en pantalla"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:177
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Simulates soft shadows that occur between nearby objects."
msgstr "Simula sombras suaves que se producen entre objetos cercanos."

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:179
#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:224
#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:241
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Low"
msgstr "Bajo"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:180
#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:225
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Medium"
msgstr "Medio"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:181
#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:226
#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:243
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "High"
msgstr "Alto"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:182
#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:244
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Ultra"
msgstr "Ultra"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:185
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Post-process"
msgstr "Post-procesado"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:186
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid ""
"Post-process modifies the image to make it look better and more realistic."
msgstr ""
"El post-procesado modifica la imagen para que tenga un aspecto mejor y más "
"realista."

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:192
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid ""
"Particle Quality|Low:Artifact occurs when a particle intersects other "
"objects.|Medium:Particle intersects objects smoothly.|High:Particle "
"intersects objects smoothly, and some objects casts their shadow to "
"particles."
msgstr ""
"Calidad de partículas|Bajo:Artefactos se producen cuando una partícula "
"intersecta otros objetos.|Medio:Las partículas intersectan objetos "
"suavemente.|Alto:Las partículas intersectan objetos suavemente, y algunos "
"objetos proyectan su sombra a las partículas."

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:199
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Volumetric Fog"
msgstr "Niebla volumétrica"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:200
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "None"
msgstr "Ninguno"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:201
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Disables the volumetric fog effect."
msgstr "Desactiva el efecto de niebla volumétrica."

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:202
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Level 1"
msgstr "Nivel 1"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:203
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Applies local illumination to the fog."
msgstr "Aplica iluminación local a la niebla."

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:204
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Level 2"
msgstr "Nivel 2"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:205
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Applies both local illumination and global illumination to the fog."
msgstr ""
"Aplica tanto la iluminación local como la iluminación global a la niebla."

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:206
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Warning: '{0}' must be enabled."
msgstr "Advertencia: '{0}' debe estar activado."

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:213
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Dynamic Lights"
msgstr "Luces dinámicas"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:214
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid ""
"Gives some objects an ability to emit light to give them an energy-emitting "
"impression."
msgstr ""
"Otorga a algunos objetos la capacidad de emitir luz para darles una "
"impresión de emisores de energía."

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:217
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Shadows"
msgstr "Sombras"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:218
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Non-static object casts a shadow."
msgstr "Los objetos no estáticos proyectan una sombra."

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:221
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Physically Based Lighting"
msgstr "Iluminación basada en la física"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:222
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid ""
"Uses more accurate approximation techniques to decide the brightness of "
"objects."
msgstr ""
"Utiliza técnicas de aproximación más precisas para decidir el brillo de los "
"objetos."

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:229
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Direct Lights"
msgstr "Luces directas"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:230
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid ""
"Controls how light encounting a material and atmosphere directly affects its "
"appearance."
msgstr ""
"Controla cómo la luz llega a un material y el ambiente afecta directamente a "
"su aspecto."

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:239
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid ""
"Water Shader|None:Water is rendered in the same way that normal blocks are "
"done.|Level 1:Refraction and the reflected Sun are simulated.|Level 2:Waving "
"water is simulated as well as reflection and refraction.|Level 3:Reflections "
"and refractions are rendered at the highest quality using screen-space "
"techniques."
msgstr ""
"Water Shader|None:Water is rendered in the same way that normal blocks are "
"done.|Level 1:Refraction and the reflected Sun are simulated.|Level 2:Waving "
"water is simulated as well as reflection and refraction.|Level 3:Reflections "
"and refractions are rendered at the highest quality using screen-space "
"techniques."

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:242
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Med"
msgstr "Med"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:247
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Shader Effects"
msgstr "Efectos del sombreador"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:248
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Special effects."
msgstr "Efectos especiales."

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:263
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid ""
"Fast Mode:Reduces the image resolution to make the rendering faster.|Off|2x|"
"4x"
msgstr ""
"Modo Rápido:Reduce la resolución de la imagen para hacer un rendimiento mas "
"rápido.|Apagado|2x|4x"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:473
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Audio Settings"
msgstr "Ajustes de audio"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:478
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Backend"
msgstr "Motor"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:481
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "OpenAL"
msgstr "OpenAL"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:487
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid ""
"Uses an OpenAL-capable sound card to process sound. In most cases where "
"there isn't such a sound card, software emulation is used."
msgstr ""
"Utiliza una tarjeta de sonido compatible con OpenAL para procesar el sonido. "
"En la mayoría de los casos en los que no existe tal tarjeta de sonido, se "
"utiliza la emulación por software."

#. ! The name of audio driver that outputs no audio.
#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:498
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Null"
msgstr "Nulo"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:501
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Disables audio output."
msgstr "Desactivar salida de audio."

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:511
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Volume"
msgstr "Volumen"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:516
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "Polyphonics"
msgstr "Polifónicos"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:518
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid ""
"Specifies how many sounds can be played simultaneously. Higher value needs "
"more processing power, so setting this too high might cause an overload "
"(especially with a software emulation)."
msgstr ""
"Especifica cuántos sonidos pueden reproducirse simultáneamente. Un valor más "
"alto necesita más potencia de procesamiento, por lo que un valor demasiado "
"alto podría causar una sobrecarga (especialmente con una emulación de "
"software)."

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:524
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid "EAX"
msgstr "EAX"

#: Resources/Scripts/Gui/StartupScreen/ConfigViewTabs.as:526
msgctxt "StartupScreen"
msgid ""
"Enables extended features provided by the OpenAL driver to create more "
"ambience."
msgstr ""
"Activa las funciones ampliadas que ofrece el controlador OpenAL para crear "
"más ambiente."

